-- ALTER VIEW kpiemail.dim_kpi_territorio
-- AS
SELECT
    [CICLO]
,[ROW_ID_TERRITORIO]
,[TFT]
,[DIAS_UTEIS]
,[VISITAS_ABATER]
,[OBJETIVO_VISITA_DIA]
,[DIAS_VISITACAO]
,[VR_CLM]
,[KEY_TERR_CICLO]
FROM
    OPENROWSET(
        BULK 'https://gsksynapseaccount.dfs.core.windows.net/gskoutputfiles/Email & KPI Visitacao/dimensao_kpi_territorio.parquet',
        FORMAT='PARQUET'
    ) with (
        [CICLO]                 VARCHAR(50) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8
,[ROW_ID_TERRITORIO]	VARCHAR(50) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8
,[TFT]					VARCHAR(50) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8
,[DIAS_UTEIS]			VARCHAR(50) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8
,[VISITAS_ABATER]		VARCHAR(50) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8
,[OBJETIVO_VISITA_DIA]	VARCHAR(50) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8
,[DIAS_VISITACAO]		VARCHAR(50) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8
,[VR_CLM]				VARCHAR(50) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8
,[KEY_TERR_CICLO]		VARCHAR(50) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8
    ) as row
